        "timestamp": "2018-08-08 16:33:59.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> The Job builder -1 this, however the build looks successful to me? \n > Am I missing something here?\n\nThe build succeeded but the job failed on lftools-install.sh - which I believe is used to copy logs from job to storage, cleanup etc. \n\nYour re check will likely fix the issue.\n\n\"\nlftools-install.sh\n14:56:50 Traceback (most recent call last):\n14:56:50   File \"/usr/lib/python3/dist-packages/virtualenv.py\", line 2363, in <module>\n14:56:50     main()\n14:56:50   File \"/usr/lib/python3/dist-packages/virtualenv.py\", line 719, in main\n14:56:50     symlink=options.symlink)\n14:56:50   File \"/usr/lib/python3/dist-packages/virtualenv.py\", line 988, in create_environment\n14:56:50     download=download,\n14:56:50   File \"/usr/lib/python3/dist-packages/virtualenv.py\", line 918, in install_wheel\n14:56:50     call_subprocess(cmd, show_stdout=False, extra_env=env, stdin=SCRIPT)\n14:56:50   File \"/usr/lib/python3/dist-packages/virtualenv.py\", line 812, in call_subprocess\n14:56:50     % (cmd_desc, proc.returncode))\n14:56:50 OSError: Command /tmp/v/lftools/bin/python2 - setuptools pkg_resources pip wheel failed with error code 2\n\"",
